Mix garlic,ginger, gochujang,gochugaru, sugar in a bowl And set aside Cut all the veggies and chicken into bite size. In a big bowl mix all the veggies and chicken with the sauce. Put it in a pan and on a high heat and put the lid on. After 3-5minutes stir it occasionally and if you feel like the veggies and chicken are cooked, then open the lid and cook until the liquid reduced. Put it on a low heat and ad some mozzarella cheese on top and put the lid on for about a minute until the cheese is melted then garnish it with some chopped scallions.
